      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "\nPedro S\xE1nchez V\xE1zquez.\n\nThis game is part of my TFG project
    in Universitat Oberta de Catalunya for my degree on Computer Science and Engineering.
    \n\nThe original game mechanics were taken from Azul boardgame by Kiesling M.
    \n\nDisclaimer: Most art in the game was AI generated using Nano Banana 2.  \n\nI
    respect the work of the wonderful artists out there that create inmersive and
    liveful gaming experiences. However, given my time restrictions and available
    resources as a student I opted for AI as a source of quick prototype images for
    the game.\n\nMusic:\nMenu: Stay by my side - Rodrigo Flores\nGame: Fields of
    Grain Piano - Jacob Lives\n\nDevelopement:\nPedro S\xE1nchez V\xE1zquez\n\n2026\n\n\n
    \n"
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
